Package Description
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent
Package that implements the agent and all the necessary classes, that let the user control it.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base
Package with classes, that are used throughout the framework.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.configuration
Class that implements all the configurations.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.console
This package manages the console.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.events
Event handling.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.exceptions
Some basic exceptions for our framework.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.framework
Basic classes, that manage the whole application.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.graphics
Package containing all the graphics we use.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.interests
Package that defines classes that represents important places on the in-game map.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.logging
This package implements classes, that we use during logging.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.server
This package implements the HTTP server (using Jetty) and classes that are used to handle the communication with dot2ai addon.
cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world
This package represents the world.
